OL,3,CJersey social housing tenants
OL,4,C'coughing up black' in mouldy Andium
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA Jersey couple claim they are
OL,8,F'coughing up black' from living in a
OL,9,Fmouldy property run by government
OL,10,Fsocial housing provider, Andium Homes.
OL,12,FLaura Richmond and Paul Hacquoil have
OL,13,Fbeen staying in damp conditions for
OL,14,Fmore than a year and say it's causing
OL,15,Fthem endless stress.
OL,17,FLaura told ITV News: "We're literally
OL,18,Fcoughing up black. In the night we
OL,19,Falways think we have a cold and then
OL,20,Fall of a sudden, we go out for a walk
OL,21,Fand it clears.
