OL,3,CJersey social housing tenants
OL,4,C'coughing up black' in mouldy Andium
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"I was ready to get back to work,
OL,8,Fready to get on with life, but it's
OL,9,Fmentally impacted me really badly and
OL,10,Fphysically, I actually deleted the
OL,11,Fpictures because they were so
OL,12,Fdisgusting."
OL,14,FThe pair are sleeping on their living
OL,15,Froom floor in their coats, because
OL,16,Ftheir bedroom feels too cold and
OL,17,Frecently had to send their dog away as
OL,18,Fthey felt he was struggling too.
