OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FPaul said: "It's very upsetting. That
OL,8,Fdog was beautiful and then started
OL,9,Fcoughing and sneezing."
OL,11,FDominique Caunce, Lead for Policy and
OL,12,FStakeholder Engagement at Andium
OL,13,FHomes, said in response: "Our clients'
OL,14,Fwellbeing is our absolute priority.
OL,15,FWe're here to help and we have a
OL,16,Fdedicated team ready to visit and
OL,17,Fcarry out any works that are required.
