OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"It's very difficult when it's mould,
OL,8,Fhumidity, condensation. Brompton Villa
OL,9,Fis one of our oldest homes but has got
OL,10,Finsulation and electric heating. It is
OL,11,Freally important that residents make
OL,12,Fsure they are ventilating and heating
OL,13,Ftheir properties in order to eradicate
OL,14,Fas much of that moisture as possible.
