OL,3,CJersey social housing tenants
OL,4,C'coughing up black' in mouldy Andium
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"We have recently installed a PIV unit
OL,8,Fthat will remove a lot of the old
OL,9,Fstagnant air and replace it with fresh
OL,10,Fair. We would expect to see huge
OL,11,Fimprovements from that very quickly.
OL,12,FWe will also be installing some
OL,13,Fsecondary glazing to the property.
OL,15,F"It is a listed building so we can't
OL,16,Freplace the windows. They've had
OL,17,Fseveral repairs over the years so we
OL,18,Fexcept now is the time to do that
OL,19,Fsecondary glazing.
