OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"(As a listed building) it certainly
OL,8,Fpresents more challenges for us but it
OL,9,Fdoesn't stop us doing work and various
OL,10,Frepairs have been carried out over the
OL,11,Fyears and the secondary glazing will
OL,12,Fbe going in soon.
OL,14,F"We have been, on average, speaking to
OL,15,Fthem twice a week since the new year.
OL,16,FWe will be going to visit them again
OL,17,Fjust to check in and see how the PIV
OL,18,Funit is working.
